messages.message: Is anyone seeing this when trying to access grafana? trying to figure out if this is a problem on my end or if others are seeing this as well
which env is this on? i’m able to access grafana on dogfood and uat
im on chrome - maybe there are other settings i need to change?
i’m able to access it on chrome and i don’t have any specific settings on :thinking_face:

@Dominic Fannjiang In all probability, you might run into this issue on any environment. I am on that boat. I thought this could be due to some cookies on Chrome or something but clearing them didn't help.

I tried using Safari and it worked. Not sure why Chrome doesn't work. I haven't tried updating Chrome yet, let me know if that works for you
ah yes safari works for me, thanks!
bring up devtools on that page, long click the refresh button and choose clear cache + hard reload. Maybe that’ll help
hard reload didn't help. upgrading chrome to latest version did.
